      "description": "Budget-friendly and priced to move, this vehicle offers an affordable entry point for a handy buyer, first-time owner, or anyone seeking a practical project. It shows wear consistent with age and use, but presents a solid value opportunity with straightforward appeal for someone who recognizes potential. A sensible choice for low-cost transportation or a weekend fixer-upper.",
